modShortDescription: This 7 Days to Die mod removes invisible animals from the world to allow more actual animals to spawn.
modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod removes invisible [animals](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-animals/) from the world to allow more actual animals to spawn.

## Changelog

* **_(new)_** Update entityclasses.xml
* Updated to B169.
* Fixed errors due to latest patch.
* **Added:**  
   * Animals to all biomes.  
   * Wasteland respawn is delayed for 7 days.
